{"tid":495683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國受污染毒米 以米粉米線的形式 大量輸入本港","createTime":"2017-12-11T02:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T03:50:57.000Z","uid":12449,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"63cdb9f69025e1e93bb51444e222dab9b0739ec2","tid":495683,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國受污染毒米 以米粉米線的形式 大量輸入本港</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每日食米粉米線，有冇諗過同慢性自殺冇分別？<br />\n<br />\n中國的食物安全問題層出不窮，<br />\n<br />\n不斷挑戰公眾想像力的極限。<br />\n<br />\n由米的種植地點到製成米粉米線，<br />\n<br />\n無論是廠房的衛生情況，還是土地水源，都離不開<span style=\"color: red;\">污染</span>兩字。<br />\n<br />\n早前已經有新聞證實其中一款東莞米粉，重金屬含量超標<br />\n<br />\n[ 2017年11月16日] <span style=\"color: red;\">孔雀牌東莞米粉重金屬鎘超標60% 食安中心籲停用</span><br />\n[ 2017年11月17日] <span style=\"color: red;\">鎘超標　孔雀牌東莞米粉回收 茶餐廳多採用</span><br />\n<br />\n我相信受污染有毒嘅米粉米線只係冰山一角。<br />\n<br />\n根據綠田園報導:「差不多 55 萬港人正在食用中國米。而且，香港人還會進食不少<span style=\"color: red;\">米製品</span>，如<span style=\"color: red;\">米粉、米線</span>、腸粉、湯圓、稯、年糕、蘿蔔糕、&hellip;&hellip;，以及粘米粉、糯米粉，原材料的產地就是中國。」<br />\n<br />\n不少香港打工仔，貪平每日進食專賣米粉米線餐廳，<br />\n<br />\n間接進食中國受污染毒米的人數，遠超過以上數目。<br />\n<br />\n米粉米線之所以便宜，正因為原材料是中國受污染毒米。<br />\n<br />\n平時食米會小心選擇揀泰國米嘅你，<br />\n<br />\n有得揀，點解仲要每日食米粉米線呢？"},{"pid":"ebf914bef8e2a9ccf08a1cdd66edf3735ba21130","tid":495683,"uid":38194,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"米線呢樣嘢不嬲比狗食"},{"pid":"63120ce67cc9cb8d2f7810b26f9df7cb071dd088","tid":495683,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"X仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生加"},{"pid":"e2cb1acd8214a20376b11b9cb081ff64babfc3d8","tid":495683,"uid":49392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"港女至愛癱仔"},{"pid":"df4781f28fd1371734ac181efc32da640d6cbac7","tid":495683,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"下，東莞米粉出事，咁仲有邊隻好食"},{"pid":"6cd750cd95f837c69c26590718bd8477a58a818b","tid":495683,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"慳返啖氣啦<br />\n華人食少陣會冚家產溶血痾爛屎遭天譴架<br />\n應該鼓勵食多d"},{"pid":"637e3a661f89591c794b7d0cffe7923d9b460002","tid":495683,"uid":113720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"JR入黎講句野啦"},{"pid":"7ab58fc398ee3657b5cdb2a5877b5309daf68f86","tid":495683,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"做飽死嘅鬼好過做餓死嘅鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2f7d0e0af2f4a5422c706fa1432203e013a03c","tid":495683,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 根據綠田園報導:「差不多 55 萬港人正在食用中國米。而且，香港人還會進食不少米製品，如米粉、米線、腸粉、湯圓、稯、年糕、蘿蔔糕、&hellip;&hellip;，以及粘米粉、糯米粉，原材料的產地就是中國。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新年咩都唔食得"},{"pid":"33b976d7e337a0d5ee355a69b3c7f2b3b38649f7","tid":495683,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下，東莞米粉出事，咁仲有邊隻好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉食意粉啦巴打"},{"pid":"cc4859006274979c2294c1caf887b29e4d78ec04","tid":495683,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote> 根據綠田園報導:「差不多 55 萬港人正在食用中國米。而且，香港人還會進食不少米製品，如米粉、米線、腸粉、湯圓、稯、年糕、蘿蔔糕、&hellip;&hellip;，以及粘米粉、糯米粉，原材料的產地就是中國。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新年咩都唔食得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺，得返屋企用泰國米整呢條路"},{"pid":"e3206cea9e1a43b58aa99727e4663fe5f2c2a77e","tid":495683,"uid":69177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下，東莞米粉出事，咁仲有邊隻好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天鵝牌，泰國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d8786ab773f9130516008b828144942367d6f8","tid":495683,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"算吧啦. 未聽過賭馬輸既人係怪馬會囉. 笑."},{"pid":"1d9ed3c7790f7db68b2092fcc94cd7376bdb3e3b","tid":495683,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下，東莞米粉出事，咁仲有邊隻好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天鵝牌，泰國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰國米靚，米粉是但一隻牌子已經夠高質"},{"pid":"e273388b9cde0ed7dc6b11c2ee89c040b2b513d3","tid":495683,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下，東莞米粉出事，咁仲有邊隻好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天鵝牌，泰國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n超力<br />\n好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d47094931900263d85fd93ab6e0432ce32821cd","tid":495683,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"本身食開泰國米粉<br />\n有次超市做優惠 送東莞米粉<br />\n一放落水煮 會溶嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且有種金屬味<br />\n貪小便宜換來短命幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911acb25115a97c3e7a9b19bff2a867717ac16c5","tid":495683,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"好彩平時都唔多食呢啲<br />\n譚仔更加未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575ae83d2ef32e55f69c1dd25785a41376c3dd01","tid":495683,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"屌成日食米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2e495a326bfa033ed151